high_descs: Turn left and walk to the far short end of the table.
Pick the salt up off the table.
Walk right and ahead to the shelves near the right wall.
Put the salt on the second to the bottom shelf.
Turn around and walk towards and past the sink to the counter next to it.
Pick up the salt that's against the wall.
Turn around and walk back to the shelving unit.
Put the salt shaker next to the other salt shaker on the shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put two salt shakers on a shelf.

high_descs: Walk towards a table to the right of the fridge.
Pick up the salt from the table.
Turn right, then turn left and walk towards a shelf.
Place the salt on the shelf.
Turn back around, and walk towards the sink.
Pick up the salt from next to the sink.
Return to the shelf on the other side of the room.
Place the salt on the shelf.
anns.task_desc: Place two salt shakers on a shelf.

high_descs: Walk over to the kitchen island, then hang a left and walk around the kitchen island to its far end.
Pick up the salt shaker that is to the left of the wine bottle on the kitchen island.
Turn right and begin walking to the oven, then hang a left and walk over to the wooden shelving unit in the corner of the room.
Place the salt shaker on the front edge of the middle shelf of the wooden shelving unit.
Turn left and walk over to the island, then turn left again and walk around the island to the kitchen sink.
Pick up the salt shaker that is closest to the microwave on the counter to the right of the sink.
Turn left and walk over to the oven, then hang a left and walk up to the wooden shelving unit in the corner of the room.
Put the salt shaker on the front edge of the middle shelf of the wooden shelving unit next to the salt shaker that is already there.
anns.task_desc: Move two salt shakers to the shelf of a wooden shelving unit.

high_descs: Head to the table in front of you, then hang a left and talk to the end of the table on the right
Pick up the salt shaker that is on the table
Turn right and walk to the cabinet, then turn left and cross the room to the brown shelf
Place the salt shaker on the middle shelf
Turn around and cross the room to the sink
Pick up the salt shaker that is against the wall to the right of the sink
Turn around and head to the brown shelf that is across the room
Place the salt shaker on the middle shelf to the right of the shaker that is already there
anns.task_desc: Place salt shakers on a shelf
